                "name": "Monster Core",
                "page": 359,
                "type": "source"
              }
            ],
            "text": "When first exposed to bright light, the monster is blinded until the end of its next turn. After this exposure, light doesn't blind the monster again until after it spends 1 hour in darkness. However, as long as the monster is in an area of bright light, it's dazzled.",
